The Democratic Alliance (DA) is saddened by the passing of veteran actress Mam’ Mary Twala. Twala was not only a legendary actress, she was a trailblazing artist whose talents were unmatched. From local television dramas to the silver screen, Mam’ Twala was a constant and unforgettable presence on our screens. She has made an immense contributions to the South African television and film industry and we will never see a talent like her again. The DA sends our heartfelt condolences to Mam’ Twala’s family, loved ones and the South African entertainment fraternity during this difficult time. Lala ngoxolo Mam’ Mary Twala